NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key_here
DATABASE_URL=your_database_url_here (ONLY NEEDED IN DEV)
DB_SCHEMA=your_db_schema_name_here (Only strictly needed in dev, make sure to set this to your own schema so you don't interfere with other devs)
PROXY_PROVIDER_ENDPOINT=endpoint_here (this needs to be inserted into ECS run time environment)
PROXY_PROVIDER_API_KEY=key_here (this needs to be inserted into ECS run time environment)
ZYTE_API_ENDPOINT=endpoint_here
ZYTE_API_KEY=key_here